                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <hr>
                <div class="row" id="contact">
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                        <div class="footer-widget">
                            <h4>About Klickit</h4>
                            <p>Klickit is a fintech company operating in the education industry. We offer a secure fees management system for educational institutions and a hassle-free payment experience for parents.</p>
